<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>Alt er vel</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 All is well, all is well
 We have heard the Message,
 Shalom, and all is well.
 There is a place of perfect rest
 behind the inner veil.
 So rest, little bride, rest for all is well

[V2]
 Alt er vel, alt er vel
 vi har hørt Hans Budskap, Shalom
 og alt er vel. Der er et sted hvor hvile
 finns, rett bak tidens mur. Så hvil lille
 Brud; hvil, for alt er vel.</lyrics>
<title>All is well</title>
<presentation>v1 v2 </presentation>
</song>